Package: catsay
Version: 1.0
Architecture: all
Maintainer: Alienkrishn [Anon4You]
Depends: git, python
Section: games
Priority: optional
Homepage: https://github.com/Anon4You/catsay
Description: terminal-based feline messenger inspired by cowsay
 A Python-based program that displays messages inside dynamic speech
 bubbles with various cat ASCII art designs. Supports custom cat
 assets and piping from other CLI tools.
